format(String, Object...) - Static method in class org.tquadrat.foundation.lang.internal.SharedFormatter
Returns a formatted String using the specified format String and arguments.

The implementation uses internally the Locale that is returned by Locale.getDefault().

This method is meant as a replacement for the method String.format(String, Object...); that implementation always uses a new instance of Formatter for each invocation.
